rows.label: xs00090100_MSG0001
rows.name:
Looks like dawn is breaking soon.
And the rain seems to be letting up, too.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs00090100_MSG0002
rows.name:
Come on.
You're about to see something interesting.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs00090100_MSG0004
rows.name: Those are this planet's native inhabitants.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs00090100_MSG0005
rows.name:
As the newcomers here, we need to make sure
we get along with them.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs00090100_MSG0007
rows.name: An unknown world, not even listed on any starcharts.[ST:wait ]
